Changes from upstream
---------------------

- Repackaged as `@precog/autocomplete-specs` for in-tree consumption.
- Added `scripts/generate-index.mjs` to produce `build/index.json` and copy
  icons into `build/icons/` so the Precog desktop overlay can serve them via
  the `spec://localhost/...` protocol with no network calls.
- No edits to the spec content itself.
